466
00:46:51.683 --> 00:46:53.177
Affedersiniz.

467
00:46:57.813 --> 00:47:00.351
Affedersiniz! Dikkat ettim de...

468
00:47:00.566 --> 00:47:02.642
Git buradan!

469
00:47:03.819 --> 00:47:08.861
