591
00:56:31.099 --> 00:56:33.969
Her neyse, en iktidarlı...

592
00:56:35.561 --> 00:56:37.637
... en şiirsel...

593
00:56:37.897 --> 00:56:39.521
... en prestijli...

594
00:56:44.320 --> 00:56:47.819
